Task: Create LedManager and unit tests
Summary of changes:
- Created include/led_manager.h and src/led_manager.cpp declaring and implementing the LedManager class.
- Supported active-low RGB LED pins (Red=GPIO 4, Green=GPIO 16, Blue=GPIO 17) and non-blocking timers.
- Mapped Wi-Fi states: Connecting (slow blink Blue), Connected (solid Green for 3s then off), Disconnected (fast blink Red).
- Mapped weather status pulses: Sunny (Yellow), Rain/Snow (Blue), Overcast/Fog (White), Thunderstorm (indefinite Red alert).
- Added setEnabled() low-power toggle.
- Extended mocks in tests/mocks/ to support pinMode/digitalWrite tracking and configurable millis.
- Created tests/test_led/test_led.cpp verifying all states, timings, and toggles pass.
